sentences.english: Unless your scuba diving equipment is up to standard, do not use it.
sentences.chinese: 如果你的水肺潛泳設備不合標準，就不要使用它。

sentences.english: Great minds think alike, but fools seldom differ.
sentences.chinese: 英雄所見略同，傻瓜很少意見不合。

sentences.english: Scholarships will be canceled for those who cannot pass the health examination.
sentences.chinese: 入學體檢不合格者，獎學金資格將被取消。

sentences.english: Any reworked non-conforming products must go through the re-inspection processes after rework.
sentences.chinese: 任何返工後的不合格品均須重新檢查。

sentences.english: But the request for “sayings” was not an unreasonable one.
sentences.chinese: 然而“驚世之語”並非不合理的請求。

sentences.english: they don't pay fair wages, their hours are inhumane,
sentences.chinese: 工資不合理，工作時間太沒人性了。

sentences.english: Specifically, a sweater that does not fit right and is very ugly.
sentences.chinese: 具體來說是一件不合身而且看起來很醜的毛衣。

sentences.english: His tone can be alarmingly inconsequential, as if the reader is there to be perpetually wrong-footed.
sentences.chinese: 他的語氣極其不合邏輯，好像讀者永遠都站不對陣腳。

sentences.english: Note that there are some combinations which may not be reasonable or desirable.
sentences.chinese: 注意，某些組合可能是不合理的，或是應該避免的。

sentences.english: Does anyone think this seems not reasonable?
This is the most fatal and most illogical social perversion that can possibly be imagined.
sentences.chinese: 這是可能想像的最致命和最不合邏輯社會反常。

sentences.english: With such a great victory come unreasonably great expectations.
sentences.chinese: 如此的重大的勝利帶來了不合理的巨大期望。

sentences.english: The difficulties with CSR come when companies get it out of proportion.
sentences.chinese: 難點在於很多公司在對於社會職責的安排不合比例。

sentences.english: In another word, the range of relating right shall not be unreasonably extended.
sentences.chinese: 換句話說，鄰接權的範圍不得被不合理的擴大。

sentences.english: The expectations of 'De Bestest Fans in de Werld Ever, Like' have become unreasonably high.
sentences.chinese: “最忠誠的球迷”對他們的期待高得不合情理。

sentences.english: About 80 percent of the decisions you make are inconsequential.
sentences.chinese: 你所做的決定中約有80%是不合理的。
